#### Search for jokes in specific category
You can search for jokes in a specific category. Categories are managed using tags in the backend. To get a [dad joke](https://jokes.one/tag/dad "Dad jokes") you can specify a parameter "category=dad".
GET /joke/search 
This would translate in to curl like the following:
curl -X GET "https://api.jokes.one/joke/search?category=dad" -H "accept: application/json" -H "content-type: application/json" -H "X-JokesOne-Api-Secret: api_key" 
The above call would return a joke in [dad jokes](https://jokes.one/tag/dad "Dad jokes") category 
